gg_open_sewer

Fight for control of the city's sewer system. This map has 44 spawns, Buy Zones, and is made for Gun Game.

-	44 Spawn points, 22 per team
-	3d Skybox
-	Compiled in HDR
-	Buy Zones
-	Optimized with No Draw
-	All files compiled into the .bsp using Pakrat

Note:  This map is not Bot friendly, recommended play with people only.

Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt - Level Design
http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/776402
